TodoListService

components.name: AppComponent
ButtonComponent

inputsClass.name: size
inputsClass.rawdescription: How large should the button be?

components.name: FormComponent
components.templateData:
<form (ngSubmit)="onSubmit(myForm)" #myForm="ngForm">
  <app-input
    for="taskTitle"
    class="input"
    label="Task:"
    type="text"
    placeholder="Add new task"
    ngModel
    ngDefaultControl
    name="taskTitle"
  ></app-input>

  <app-button
    id="hi"
    [primary]="true"
    type="submit"
    class="button-add"
    label="Add"
    size="large"
    borderRadius="0.25rem"
  ></app-button>
</form>
